[SPEAKER_00] u ono vrijeme da je David imao pornografiju,

735
01:05:11,679 --> 01:05:12,219
[SPEAKER_00] to bi bilo to.

736
01:05:12,219 --> 01:05:14,320
[SPEAKER_00] Gleda Betšebu kako se svlači i tamo.

737
01:05:14,320 --> 01:05:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ubio čovjeka.

738
01:05:14,880 --> 01:05:15,739
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vojarista.

739
01:05:15,739 --> 01:05:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] I onda uzeo je k sebi,

740
01:05:17,880 --> 01:05:19,019
[SPEAKER_00] ubio čovjeka,

741
01:05:19,019 --> 01:05:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, reči gore od toga.

742
01:05:20,159 --> 01:05:20,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, znaš šta?

743
01:05:20,920 --> 01:05:22,400
[SPEAKER_00] David je preuzio odgovornost.

744
01:05:22,400 --> 01:05:24,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ponavljam,

745
01:05:24,039 --> 01:05:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] ljudski je past,

746
01:05:24,960 --> 01:05:25,860
[SPEAKER_00] i svi ćemo past,

747
01:05:25,860 --> 01:05:28,059
[SPEAKER_00] ali preuzmi odgovornost čovječe.

748
01:05:28,059 --> 01:05:29,940
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to bi bila ta treća stvar.

749
01:05:29,940 --> 01:05:31,280
[SPEAKER_00] Neodgovornost.

750
01:05:31,280 --> 01:05:33,280
[SPEAKER_00] To su moje neke,

751
01:05:33,280 --> 01:05:35,340
