752
01:05:35,340 --> 01:05:37,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bi ušao sad u pojedine grijehe,

753
01:05:37,519 --> 01:05:41,719
[SPEAKER_00] ali to su te tri neodgovornost.

754
01:05:41,719 --> 01:05:43,179
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, to je onaj dio,

755
