784
01:06:37,260 --> 01:06:38,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, napravio sam grešku.

785
01:06:39,219 --> 01:06:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, sada idemo dalje.

786
01:06:40,559 --> 01:06:42,980
[SPEAKER_00] I ja skidam kapu tom čovjeku.

787
