01:09:42,239 --> 01:09:44,159
[SPEAKER_01] nema tu kraljevsku čast i dimenziju.

850
01:09:44,159 --> 01:09:46,680
[SPEAKER_01] Osjećam da ne vladam sobom.

851
01:09:46,680 --> 01:09:49,100
[SPEAKER_01] I sad ti meni govoriš, okreni se budućnosti,

852
01:09:49,100 --> 01:09:50,939
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam u rasulu, raspadu, ne znam,

853
01:09:51,460 --> 01:09:52,720
[SPEAKER_01] imam problema s bilo čim,

